# Each Affix comes with a standard, pre-generated line:
# "{1}{0} to stat"
# The {0} is the value of the affix, and the {1} is the sign.
# An in-game line would look like: -5.58 to stat
IncreasedDamageAffix.Description: "{1}{0}% daño"
DefenseItemAffix.Description: "{1}{0} defensa"
EnduranceItemAffix.Description: "{1}{0}% incrementa tu resistencia al daño"
